Package: amrcartography
Title: Tools for Antimicrobial Resistance Cartography
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Andrew", "Balmer", email = "ab69@sanger.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("OpenAI", role = "ctb")
  )
Description: Infrastructure for turning the AMR cartography analysis workflow
    into a reproducible R package. The current package provides source-data
    manifests, example-data download helpers, phenotype and genotype
    preprocessing helpers for the S. pneumoniae case study, and utilities for
    multidimensional scaling workflows used in AMR cartography analyses.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
